commands: jq --arg buildroot "$FLATPAK_BUILDER_BUILDDIR" --argjson data '{"github:tauri-apps/tauri-plugin-log#v1": "flatpak-node/git-packages/tauri-plugin-log-api-19f5dcc0425e9127d2c591780e5047b83e77a7c2#19f5dcc0425e9127d2c591780e5047b83e77a7c2"}' 'walk(    if type == "object"    then        to_entries | map(            if (.value | type == "string") and $data[.value]            then .value = "git+file:\($buildroot)/\($data[.value])"            else .            end        ) | from_entries    else .    end)' $FLATPAK_BUILDER_BUILDDIR/package.json > $FLATPAK_BUILDER_BUILDDIR/package.json.new

jq --arg buildroot "$FLATPAK_BUILDER_BUILDDIR" --argjson data '{"https://github.com/tauri-apps/tauri-plugin-log.git#19f5dcc0425e9127d2c591780e5047b83e77a7c2": "flatpak-node/git-packages/tauri-plugin-log-api-19f5dcc0425e9127d2c591780e5047b83e77a7c2#19f5dcc0425e9127d2c591780e5047b83e77a7c2", "ssh://git@github.com/tauri-apps/tauri-plugin-log.git#19f5dcc0425e9127d2c591780e5047b83e77a7c2": "flatpak-node/git-packages/tauri-plugin-log-api-19f5dcc0425e9127d2c591780e5047b83e77a7c2#19f5dcc0425e9127d2c591780e5047b83e77a7c2"}' 'walk(    if type == "object" and (.version | type == "string") and $data[.version]    then        .version = "git+file:\($buildroot)/\($data[.version])"    else .    end)' $FLATPAK_BUILDER_BUILDDIR/package-lock.json > $FLATPAK_BUILDER_BUILDDIR/package-lock.json.new
